{"tid":874641,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人屋企近排勁多呢啲蟲?","createTime":"2018-10-24T10:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T12:38:16.000Z","uid":71320,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"887cf32c12547fd252a2ecd3fe83d710cc02bd24","tid":874641,"uid":71320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:45:21.000Z","msg":"本來一開始諗住一兩隻 唔鬼理佢<br />\n頭先睇睇下電視飛入埋我耳仔度 痕到仆街<br />\n頂佢唔順 好鬼煩<br />\n已經殺左十幾隻 殺極都有<br />\n有冇人知係咩蟲 點先可以解決到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/184447_1123c490d1629917bd9ad5c841e5c2fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F184447_1123c490d1629917bd9ad5c841e5c2fa.jpg&h=bd5d399c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/184450_2c90ca11d2764941a2339de400114d13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F184450_2c90ca11d2764941a2339de400114d13.jpg&h=1ed17269&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/184455_f5f4f220cba0f6288318277f12d3b421.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F184455_f5f4f220cba0f6288318277f12d3b421.jpg&h=a2158f2a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffc549979c8fa6e4d71534c6d2b7c5b40a423158","tid":874641,"uid":17004,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:48:43.000Z","msg":"好似係關中藥事 佢地食中藥（好似係<br />\n我試過彈佢落地會聽到有聲 勁硬淨佢地"},{"pid":"e4597e5021e0dab6ded7323eafd0192aace7b1b0","tid":874641,"uid":71320,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:49:32.000Z","msg":"又殺多兩隻"},{"pid":"fe2cb63a11870228fe0c9208dbeda2b8e7371044","tid":874641,"uid":71320,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ffc549979c8fa6e4d71534c6d2b7c5b40a423158","tid":874641,"uid":17004,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:48:43.000Z","ms